\id ZEP - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020
\h Zefania
\toc1 Zefania
\toc2 Zefania
\toc3 Zef
\mt1 Zefania
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ma e wach mar Jehova Nyasaye mane obiro ne Zefania wuod Kushi, ma wuod Gedalia, ma wuod Amaria, ma wuod Hezekia e kinde loch Josia wuod Amon ruodh Juda.
\b
\s1 Siem kuom kum mabiro
\q1 
\v 2 “Abiro tieko gik moko duto
\q2 mantie e piny mi lal nono,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\q1 
\v 3 “Abiro tieko dhano kaachiel gi le,
\q2 bende abiro tieko winy mafuyo e kor polo,
\q2 kaachiel gi rech manie nam.
\q1 Jomaricho biro pie pidhe pidhe,
\q2 e ndalo manatiek dhano e wangʼ piny,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
\s1 Kum mar jo-Juda
\q1 
\v 4 “Abiro kumo jo-Juda
\q2 kaachiel gi ji duto modak Jerusalem.
\q1 Abiro tieko jo-Baal duto mane odongʼ ka,
\q2 mi agol oko nying joma luwo nyiseche mopa kaachiel gi jodologi.
\q1 
\v 5 Bende abiro tieko ji duto makulore ewi tat udi
\q2 kalamo chiengʼ, dwe gi sulwe.
\q1 Ji duto makulore ka kwongʼore gi nying Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 to bangʼe gikwongʼore gi nying Molek nyasach jo-Amon.
\q1 
\v 6 Ji duto moseweyo luwo Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 kendo ok gimany Jehova Nyasaye kata mana penje wach.”
\b
\q1 
\v 7 Lingʼuru e nyim Jehova Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto;
\q2 nikech odiechiengʼ mar Jehova Nyasaye chiegni.
\q1 Jehova Nyasaye oseloso misango,
\q2 kendo osepwodho joma oseluongo.
\b
\q1 
\v 8 “E odiechiengʼ mitimoe misango mar Jehova Nyasaye
\q2 abiro kumo joka ruoth,
\q2 yawuot ruoth,
\q1 kaachiel gi ji duto morwakore
\q2 gi lewni mag jopinje mamoko.
\q1 
\v 9 Chiengʼno,
\q2 anakum ji duto mamiel e laru mar dino cham,
\q1 kendo mapongʼo hekalu mar nyiseche manono
\q2 gi timbe mahundu kod wuond.”
\b
\q1 
\v 10 Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Chiengʼno,
\q2 ywak noywagre koa e rangach miluongo ni Dhoranga Rech,
\q2 nduru noa e bath dala koma nyien,
\q2 kendo koko nogore matek koa e gode.
\q1 
\v 11 Gouru nduru un joma odak e mier moluoro chiro,
\q2 johala mau madongo duto ibiro yweyo oko,
\q2 kendo ji duto maloko ohand pesa notiek pep.
\q1 
\v 12 E ndalono abiro menyo Jerusalem gi teche
\q2 ka akumo joma odak kanyo madhi nyime gi timo timbe maricho,
\q2 ma gin joma chalo mana gi divai mawach;
\q1 ka giparo ni, ‘Jehova Nyasaye ok notim
\q2 gimoro amora maber kata marach.’
\q1 
\v 13 Mwandugi noyaki
\q2 kendo utegi nomuki.
\q1 Gibiro gero udi,
\q2 to ok ginidagie,
\q1 bende gibiro pitho puothe mzabibu
\q2 to ok gini madh divai moa kuomgi.”
\s1 Odiechiengʼ maduongʼ mar Jehova Nyasaye
\q1 
\v 14 “Odiechiengʼ maduongʼ mar Jehova Nyasaye chiegni,
\q2 adier ochiegni kendo obiro piyo.
\q1 Chik iti!
\q2 Ywagruok e odiechieng Jehova Nyasaye nobed malit,
\q2 kendo jolweny bende nogo koko kanyo.
\q1 
\v 15 Odiechiengʼno nobed odiechieng mirima,
\q2 enobed odiechieng mwodo lak kod rem malit,
\q1 bende enobed odiechieng chandruok gi kethruok,
\q2 enobed odiechiengʼ mopongʼ gi boche polo moimore,
\q2 kendo odiechiengʼ mopongʼ gi rumbi kod mudho.
\q1 
\v 16 To bende enobed odiechieng turumbete kod sigich mar lweny
\q2 nowinjre e mier madongo mochiel motegno,
\q2 kod ute mabeyo mag rito dala.
\b
\q1 
\v 17 “Abiro kelo luoro kod achiedh-nade kuom oganda
\q2 kendo gibiro wuotho mana ka muofni,
\q2 nikech gisetimo richo e nyim Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 Rembgi nochwer piny
\q2 kendo nyimbiye igi nopukre oko ka ngʼwe.
\q1 
\v 18 To kata mana fedha mathoth kod dhahabu ma gin-go
\q2 ok noresgi,
\q2 odiechiengʼ mar mirimb Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 Chiengʼ ma Jehova Nyasaye ngʼadoe bura,
\q2 nyiego mager ma en-go nowangʼ piny duto, mitiek pep.”
\b
\q1 Kamano e kaka notiek gik moko duto
\q2 modak e piny mana kadiemo wangʼ.
\c 2
\s1 Juda kod Jerusalem ongʼadnigi bura machalre gi ogendini mamoko
\s2 Owachne Juda mondo opwodhre kuom richo
\q1 
\v 1 Yaye un oganda maonge wichkuotni,
\q2 chokreuru kaachiel, chokreuru kaachiel,
\q1 
\v 2 ka ndalo moseyier pok ochopo
\q2 en odiechiengʼ ma ibiro teroue kuma bor ka mihudhwe mar cham.
\q1 Adier, chokreuru kapok mirima mager mar Jehova Nyasaye obiro kuomu,
\q2 kata kapok odiechiengʼ mar mirimbe ochopo.
\q1 
\v 3 Dwaruru Jehova Nyasaye, un ji duto mobolore manie piny,
\q2 kendo un ji duto matimo gik ma chik dwaro.
\q1 Dwaruru tim makare, kendo beduru gi chuny mobolore,
\q2 nimar dipo ka uyudo kar konyruok,
\q2 odiechiengno ma Jehova Nyasaye biro olo mirimbe kuom ji.
\s2 Kum mar jo-Filistia
\q1 
\v 4 Ji biro dar Gaza,
\q2 kendo Ashkelon biro dongʼ gunda.
\q1 Odiechiengʼ tir Ashdod ibiro weyo nono
\q2 kendo Ekron ibiro pudh gi tiende.
\q1 
\v 5 Yaye jo-Kereth modak e dho nam,
\q2 mano kaka unune malit,
\q1 yaye Kanaan, piny jo-Filistia,
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye nikodu gi wach kama:
\q1 “Abiro tieko chuth
\q2 kendo onge ngʼama nodongʼ.”
\q1 
\v 6 Piny mantiere e dho nam kama jo-Kereth odakie biro bedo kar jokwath
\q2 kendo kama ogerie abich rombe.
\q1 
\v 7 Nobedi mar joma odongʼ mar dhood Juda;
\q2 kanyo gini yudie lek ma gikwae.
\q1 Godhiambo gibiro nindo
\q2 e ute mag Ashkelon.
\q1 Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachgi biro ritogi
\q2 kendo obiro dwokonegi gweth mane ogwedhogigo.
\s2 Kum mar jo-Moab kod jo-Amon
\q1 
\v 8 “Asewinjo ayenje mag jo-Moab
\q2 kod ajara mag jo-Amon,
\q1 moseyanyo joga
\q2 kendo obwogogi e lopgi.”
\q1 
\v 9 Kuom mano,
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye Maratego, ma Nyasach Israel osingore kawacho kama,
\q1 “Adiera, Moab biro chalo gi Sodom,
\q2 to jo-Amon kaka Gomora,
\q1 piny modongʼ gunda
\q2 mojwangʼ motimo bunge.
\q1 Joga modongʼ noyakgi;
\q2 kendo oganda modongʼ nokaw pinygi.”
\b
\q1 
\v 10 Ma e kum ma jogi nonwangʼ kuom sunga margi,
\q2 kendo kuom yanyo kendo jaro jo-Jehova Nyasaye Maratego.
\q1 
\v 11 Jehova Nyasaye biro bedo nigi malich
\q2 ka oketho nyiseche duto e piny.
\q1 Ogendini duto modak e alwora mar dho nembe duto nolame,
\q2 ngʼato ka ngʼato nolame e pinygi owuon.
\s2 Kum mar jo-Kush
\q1 
\v 12 “Yaye jo-Kush,
\q2 un bende liganglana biro negou.”
\s2 Kum mar jo-Asuria
\q1 
\v 13 Enorie bade kuomu un joma odak yo nyandwat,
\q2 kendo notiek Asuria,
\q1 bende dala mar Nineve nodongʼ gunda
\q2 mi nobed motwo ka piny motimo ongoro.
\q1 
\v 14 Kweth mag jamni biro nindo piny motimo kanyo,
\q2 kod kit chwech mopogore opogore.
\q1 Tula mar thim kod agak
\q2 nobed gi nyasi.
\q1 Ywakgi nowinjre ka wuok gie dirisni,
\q2 kite moger godo udi nomukre mabiwre e dhoudi,
\q2 kendo sirni nodongʼ kongʼiengore.
\q1 
\v 15 Ma e dala maduongʼ mane odak gi kwe,
\q2 kendo kogalore.
\q1 Ne owacho e chunye niya,
\q2 “An e kende kendo onge ngʼama ipimo koda.”
\q1 To mano kaka koro odongʼ gunda,
\q2 kama le mag bungu yweyoe.
\q1 Ji duto makadho bute
\q2 wuoro ka tangʼo lwetgi.
\c 3
\s2 Chal mar Jerusalem e ndalo mabiro
\q1 
\v 1 Mano kaka inine malit in dala maduongʼ ma jasand ji,
\q2 ma toke tek kendo mogak.
\q1 
\v 2 Dalani ok winj puonj ngʼato angʼata,
\q2 kendo ok owinj kata puonj mora amora.
\q1 Ok ogeno kuom Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 bende ok osud machiegni gi Nyasache.
\q1 
\v 3 Jotende gin sibuoche maruto,
\q2 to ruodhige chalo gi ondiegi mawuotho gotieno,
\q2 ma ok we gimoro amora miyudi gokinyi.
\q1 
\v 4 Jonabi mage gin josunga,
\q2 kendo gin joma wuondore.
\q1 Jodolo mage njawo kama ler mar lemo,
\q2 kendo giketho chik.
\q1 
\v 5 To Jehova Nyasaye mantie e diergi, to en ngʼat makare,
\q2 ok otim gimoro amora marach.
\q1 Okinyi ka okinyi to ongʼado bura gi adier,
\q2 kendo odiechiengʼ ka odiechiengʼ ok rem,
\q2 to kata kamano, jaricho to onge wichkuot.
\s2 Jerusalem otamore pwodhore kuom richo
\q1 
\v 6 “Asengʼado ogendini oko,
\q2 kuondegi ma gigengʼorego bende asemuko.
\q1 Yoregi osedongʼ nono,
\q2 maonge ngʼama wuothoe.
\q1 Miechgi madongo osekethi;
\q2 maonge ngʼama nodongʼ kodakie kata achiel.
\q1 
\v 7 Ne awachone dala maduongʼ niya,
\q2 ‘Adier ibiro luora,
\q2 kendo ibiro yie gi puonjna!’
\q1 Ka itimo kamano, to kar dakni ok nongʼad oko,
\q2 kendo ok anakume.
\q1 Kata kamano, ne pod gi timo sinani
\q2 mar timo gik maricho.”
\q1 
\v 8 Kuom mano, Jehova Nyasaye wacho niya, “Emomiyo koro rita,
\q2 nyaka ndalo ma anangʼadnie bura.
\q1 Asechano mondo achok ogendini
\q2 gi pinjeruodhi,
\q1 mondo aol mirimba kuomgi,
\q2 ma en mirimba mager.
\q1 Piny ngima ibiro wangʼo
\q2 gi mach mar mirimba mager.
\s1 Israel biro keto genogi kuom Jehova Nyasaye
\q1 
\v 9 “Bangʼe anapwodh dho oganda
\q2 mondo giduto giluong nying Jehova Nyasaye,
\q2 kendo gitine gi chuny achiel.
\q1 
\v 10 Joga malama
\q2 kendo moke e pinje loka aore mag Kush,
\q2 nobi kakelona mich.
\q1 
\v 11 E odiechiengʼno ok inichak ine wichkuot
\q2 kaluwore gi timbe maricho mane itimona,
\q1 nikech abiro golo
\q2 josunga mamor gi sungagi e dala maduongʼni.
\q1 Ok inichak isungri kendo,
\q2 e goda maler.
\q1 
\v 12 To anawe joma muol
\q2 e dieru kendo ma obolore,
\q2 ma gin jogo ma oyie kuom nying Jehova Nyasaye.
\q1 
\v 13 Jo-Israel modongʼ ok notim gima rach,
\q2 ok giniriambi,
\q2 bende miriambo ok nowuog e dhogi.
\q1 Gibiro chiemo kendo nindo
\q2 maonge ngʼama nomi gibed maluor.”
\b
\q1 
\v 14 Wer, yaye nyar Sayun,
\q2 go koko matek, yaye Israel!
\q1 Bed mamor kendo moil gi chunyi duto,
\q2 yaye nyar Jerusalem!
\q1 
\v 15 Jehova Nyasaye osegolo kuomi kum mosekumigo
\q2 bende oseriembo wasika.
\q1 Jehova Nyasaye, ma en Ruodh jo-Israel ni kodi
\q2 ok inichak iluor gimoro amora manyalo hinyi.
\q1 
\v 16 Odiechiengʼno ji nowach ni Jerusalem niya,
\q2 “Kik iluor, yaye Sayun,
\q2 kik iwe badi obed mobengni.
\q1 
\v 17 Jehova Nyasaye ma Nyasachi ni kodi,
\q2 en gi teko mar reso ji.
\q1 Obiro bedo gi mor maduongʼ kuomi,
\q2 kendo obiro kweyo chunyi gi herane,
\q2 bende obiro wer ka omor gi ilo kuomi.”
\b
\q1 
\v 18 “Abiro golo kuomi
\q2 masiche mane ochan ni biro timore kuomi e kinde mag sewni moyier,
\q2 nikech gisebedo tingʼ mapek kuomi kendo gisemiyi wichkuot.
\q1 
\v 19 E kindeno anakum
\q2 jogo mane osandi,
\q1 anakony rongʼonde
\q2 kendo anachok joga mane oke e pinje.
\q1 Abiro miyogi pak gi huma
\q2 e piny ka piny mane okuodie wigi.
\q1 
\v 20 E kindeno abiro choki,
\q2 e ndalono anakeli dala.
\q1 Abiro miyi pak gi huma,
\q2 e kind ogendini manie piny mangima,
\q1 ka adwokoni gweth mane agwedhigo chon
\q2 mana ka ineno,”
\q2 Jehova Nyasaye owacho.
